	"description": "In this article, we are going to build a blog with Gatsby and Netlify CMS. You\nwill learn how to install Gatsby on your computer and use it to quickly develop\na super fast blog site.\n\nYou are also going to learn how to add Netlify CMS to your site by creating and\nconfiguring files, then connecting the CMS to your site through user\nauthentication. \n\nAnd finally, you&#x27;ll learn how to access the CMS admin so that you can write your\nfirst blog post.\n\nThe complete code for this project can be found he",
